DALEK ATTACK:

        After you reach London, type any of the following during play:

            PARIS-"DAY OF RECKONING"        TOKYO-"TRICOLOUR COFFEE SHOP"
            NEW YORK-"THE SLYTHER"        SKARO"D5 GAMMA Z ALPHA"

                                (INVICIBILITY)

              "JAMES BOND AND OLIVER REED WERE NEVER GOOD SINGERS"

                                (INFINITE LIVES)

        "TRUE I AM GUILTY OF INTERFERENCE JUST AS YOU ARE GUILTY OF FAILING
         TO USE YOUR GREAT POWERS" Space in between all words.

                                    (????)

                                "ESCAPE SWITCH"

        To get from the caves to the city, kill the Super Dalek and enter
        the empty room.  Now use your grenades to blow away the floor to
        reveal the way to the city.
